            <title>[HBASE-2813] Remove requirement for ssh to do non-distributed mode</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2813</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It seems we require SSH even for non-distributed mode.  Is it possible to not use SSH and thus not require it, just for the simple local box environment?  (rburton up on irc brought this up)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
